"""
PART III Income

15. Income for the purposes of the Act

(4)

Editorial note: current text valid from 2025-03-21.

The adjustments specified in this paragraph are those made in accordance with—

(f)

section 45B or 55B of the Social Security Contributions and Benefits Act 1992 (reduction of additional pension in Category A retirement pension and shared additional pension: pension sharing).
"""

adjustment_made_in_accordance_with_section_45b_of_the_social_security_contributions_and_benefits_act_1992:
    entity: Person
    period: Day
    dtype: Boolean

adjustment_made_in_accordance_with_section_55b_of_the_social_security_contributions_and_benefits_act_1992:
    entity: Person
    period: Day
    dtype: Boolean

adjustment_is_specified_in_this_paragraph_15_4_f:
    entity: Person
    period: Day
    dtype: Boolean
    from 2025-03-21:
        adjustment_made_in_accordance_with_section_45b_of_the_social_security_contributions_and_benefits_act_1992 or adjustment_made_in_accordance_with_section_55b_of_the_social_security_contributions_and_benefits_act_1992
